Project Context for AI Agent

The goal of this project is to create custom 3D objects for a board game. The game includes multiple **figures** and **obstacles**.

Design rules:

- Each item (figure or obstacle) has a **default 3D design**.
- Every design must support **two color variants** to differentiate players (similar to black and white in chess).
- Figures can also have **multiple skins** (alternative visual designs).
- Each skin must also include **two color variants** for the two players.
- Obstacles may optionally have skins, but they always follow the same color-variant rule if skins exist.

Structure:

- Item (Figure or Obstacle)
  - Default Design
    - Color Variant A (Player 1)
    - Color Variant B (Player 2)

  - Skins (optional, multiple)
    - Skin 1
      - Color Variant A
      - Color Variant B

    - Skin 2
      - Color Variant A
      - Color Variant B
